# Veris build context — excluded from `veris env push` uploads.
#
# The runtime image only needs files from `.veris/` (the Dockerfile,
# openclaw.json, and the Python wrapper). Everything else in the
# openclaw repo is irrelevant to the sandbox, so exclude-by-default
# and allowlist `.veris/` to keep the upload tiny.
*
!.veris
!.veris/**
